| Mistral-Nemo-Instruct-2407 | ✓ | ✗ | → new handler ✓ |
| Ministral-3-14B-Reasoning | ✓ | ✓ | caught earlier by existing Ministral-3 check |
| Devstral-Small-2507 | ✓ | ✓ | caught earlier by existing Ministral-3 check |
| All other templates | no `[INST]` or has `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` | — | unaffected |

